Good_Luck.help: Boosts your Defense to all attacks by 25% for 60 seconds.
Good_Luck.targetHelp: Boosts your Defense to all attacks by 25% for 60 seconds.
Good_Luck.attackerHit: You now have {PowerName} and increase your Defense.

Rugged.help: Increases all your Damage Resistance by 15% for 60 seconds. Rugged also protects you from enemy Teleportation.
Rugged.attackerHit: You are Rugged and take less damage from attacks and can resist enemy Teleportation.

Keen_Insight.help: Makes your attacks 18.75% more accurate and increases your Perception by 33% for 60 seconds.
Keen_Insight.targetHelp: Makes your attacks 18.75% more accurate and increases your Perception by 33% for 60 seconds.
Keen_Insight.attackerHit: You have {PowerName} into your enemies' weakness and increase your chance To Hit and your Perception.

Dramatic_Improvement.attackerHit: You undergo a {PowerName} and gain Hit Points.

Focused_Rage.help: Increases all your damage by 33% for 60 seconds.
Focused_Rage.attackerHit: Your {PowerName} allows you to strike with more damage.

Strength_of_Will.help: Moderately boosts your resistance to Immobilization, Sleep, Disorient and Hold effects for 180 seconds. Must be used before you are Slept, Held or Disoriented, but can be used after being Immobilized.
Strength_of_Will.targetHelp: Moderately boosts your resistance to Immobilization, Sleep, Disorient and Hold effects for 180 seconds. Must be used before you are Slept, Held or Disoriented, but can be used after being Immobilized.
Strength_of_Will.attackerHit: Your {PowerName} protects you from Immobilization, Sleep, Disorient, and Hold effects.

Emerge.help: Frees you from many Sleep, Hold, Immobilization, Disorient, Fear, Confuse and KnockBack effects and boosts your resistance to Repel, Taunt and Placate effects for 60 seconds. This Inspiration can be used even while under such effects.
Emerge.targetHelp: Frees you from many Sleep, Hold, Immobilization, Disorient, Fear, Confuse and KnockBack effects and boosts your resistance to Repel, Taunt and Placate effects for 60 seconds. This Inspiration can be used even while under such effects.
Emerge.attackerHit: You are now able to Emerge from most effects.

Bounce_Back.help: If you are defeated, you can wake up with 1/2 of your hit points. You will, however, be Disoriented, have no Endurance, and unable to recover Endurance for 10 seconds, but you will be protected from XP Debt for 15 seconds.
Bounce_Back.targetHelp: You have Bounced Back. You are Disoriented and cannot recovery Endurance. However, you are protected from XP Debt for 15 seconds.
Bounce_Back.attackerHit: You {PowerName} from the brink of death. You feel weak and cannot do anything for a while.
